A quick quality meal. Instead of just microwaved frozen junk "food" common at many fastfood eateries,  WPE uses quality fresh ingredients that  are enjoyably evident. Both indoor/outdoor tables are available so you can consume on the spot or they efficiently package your order conveniently for takeaway. They are the one stable food outlet on that block while their neighbors are constantly changing, so they have proven their worth. The menu isn't huge but the selection is tasty and you don't later feel like you ate a pound of lead. Good for a light meal.
